<p><cs><col><b>Scrimping bar</b></col>, <cd>a device used in connection
with a calico printing machine for stretching the fabric breadthwise so
that it may be smooth for printing.</cd>
<rj><au>Knight.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

